summary: AN ORDINANCE providing for the acquisition by condemnation of certain property and property rights in a portion of State Addition No. 4; Southeast one-quarter of Section 31, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M.; Southeast one-quarter of Section 30, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M. and supplemental plat of Dumar's Highland Park Addition required for certain additions and betterments (S.W. Kenyon St., et al; Sanitary Sewers) to the existing Municipal Sewerage Utility.
